Overrides special infected targeting players.
  * ignore player who is pinned by smoker & hunter.
  * change target to nearest survivor no matter vomited survivors, vomited specials, incapped, pinned etc.

Original plugin: https://forums.alliedmods.net/showthread.php?p=2680135

-Change Log-
1.2 (21-Jan-2020) by Harry
	- ignore player who is pinned by smoker & hunter.
	- change target to nearest survivor no matter anyone gets vomited.
	
1.1 (14-Jan-2020)
	- Fixed invalid entity. Thanks to "Venom1777" for reporting.

1.0 (13-Jan-2020)
	- Initial release.
  
-command-
"l4d_target_patch_allow",			"1",		"0=Plugin off, 1=Plugin on.", CVAR_FLAGS );
l4d_target_patch_modes",			"",			"Turn on the plugin in these game modes, separate by commas (no spaces). (Empty = all).", CVAR_FLAGS );
"l4d_target_patch_modes_off",		"",			"Turn off the plugin in these game modes, separate by commas (no spaces). (Empty = none).", CVAR_FLAGS );
"l4d_target_patch_modes_tog",		"0",		"Turn on the plugin in these game modes. 0=All, 1=Coop, 2=Survival, 4=Versus, 8=Scavenge. Add numbers together.", CVAR_FLAGS );
"l4d_target_patch_targets",			"12",		"0=Off. Block these Special Infected from targeting incapped players: 1=Smoker, 2=Boomer, 4=Hunter, 8=Tank, 15=All. Add numbers together.", CVAR_FLAGS );
"l4d_target_patch_version",			"1.2", 		"Target Patch plugin version."
